---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Container from "../components/ui/Container.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Contact | Old Dog, New Flex" description="Get in touch with Old Dog, New Flex">
  <section class="pt-16 pb-20">
    <Container size="sm">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue mb-4">Get in touch</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-subtext0 mb-10">
        Email is the best way to reach me. I read everything, though I can't always respond quickly.
      </p>

      <a
        href="mailto:raymond@olddognewflex.com"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg bg-surface0 border border-surface1 hover:border-mauve/50 text-text transition-colors text-lg font-medium"
      >
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><rect width="20" height="16" x="2" y="4" rx="2"/><path d="m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7"/></svg>
        raymond@olddognewflex.com
      </a>

      <div class="mt-12 space-y-4 text-subtext0">
        <p><strong class="text-text">Good reasons to write:</strong> feedback on something you read, a question the writing raised, or just to say the site is (or isn't) useful to you.</p>
        <p><strong class="text-text">Please don't:</strong> pitch products, send newsletters, or ask me to add a link. I don't respond to those.</p>
      </div>
    </Container>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
